********************************
    HELPFILE for skymatch
********************************

Match sky in overlapping exposures.

Inputs
======

input
    FLT image(s) with to match.

skyfunc
    Function for sky calculations.
    
    mean   -- Clipped mean.
    median -- Clipped median.
    mode   -- Clipped mode.

nclip
    Number of clipping iterations for sky calculations.

logfile
    Store log in this file.
    If not given, will print to screen.
